data.text:
The daily opening times of Manchester Museum in Manchester

The following overview lists the visiting hours for Manchester Museum in Manchester. The hours of the current day (today) are highlighted. Please note that opening hours on special days or holidays may differ from what is displayed here. We therefore recommend you to always check the opening hours with Manchester Museum before your visit and see if it might be needed to reserve a time slot.
